    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks for that. I've noticed some people in legal circles argue that this interpretation of substantive due process is actually kind of problematic or goes too far. How would you describe the main criticisms or the alternative view that focuses more on procedural due process?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
